<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 06:09:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯还是人质？以色列军队为加沙的两个相互冲突的目标而苦恼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/hamas-or-hostages-israeli-army-agonizes-over-two-conflicting-goals-in-gaza/0000018d-13e2-dd15-a7af-9fef130b0000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的战时内阁在如何最好地确保被俘以色列人获释的问题上陷入了困境，他们的生命危险与日俱增。 如果甘茨和艾森科特推翻紧急政府（这种可能性越来越大），可能会引发一场以色列街头掀起大规模抗议浪潮</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 04:03:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/hamas-or-hostages-israeli-army-agonizes-over-two-conflicting-goals-in-gaza/0000018d-13e2-dd15-a7af-9fef130b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：两名士兵在加沙北部丧生；卡塔尔表示周三将为以色列人质提供药品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article-live/kibbutz-beeri-announces-the-deaths-of-israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi/0000018d-156d-d260-aded-b7edc14d0000</link><description>贝埃里基布兹宣布以色列人质伊泰·斯维尔斯基和约西·沙拉比死亡 ■ 以色列总统将出席达沃斯世界经济论坛，为新的人质协议“增加政治压力” ■ 美国国务卿布林肯表示，“如果”阿拉伯国家不会重建加沙■ 沙特阿拉伯外长表示，如果巴勒斯坦问题得到解决，沙特将承认以色列 ■ 美国袭击也门胡塞武装目标 ■ 在加沙被捕的伊斯兰圣战组织指挥官称该组织成员在伊朗接受训练 ■ 以色列国防军公布在加沙阵亡的预备役军人姓名；预备役士兵在加沙战斗中受伤身亡 ■ 以色列南部商店遭火箭弹袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 03:26:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article-live/kibbutz-beeri-announces-the-deaths-of-israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi/0000018d-156d-d260-aded-b7edc14d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列卫生部继续发放枪支许可证，却在心理健康检查上磨蹭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-dawdles-on-mental-health-checks-as-ministry-continues-to-dole-out-gun-permits/0000018d-141e-dd15-a7af-9e7ff8620000</link><description>国家安全部尚未对申请携带武器许可证的以色列人实施更广泛、更详细的调查问卷</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 23:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-dawdles-on-mental-health-checks-as-ministry-continues-to-dole-out-gun-permits/0000018d-141e-dd15-a7af-9e7ff8620000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔证实：为以色列人质提供的药品将于周三进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/qatar-confirms-medicine-for-israeli-hostages-will-enter-gaza-on-wednesday/0000018d-141e-d260-aded-b7be3dd40000</link><description>多哈斡旋协议的细节仍不明确，但以色列已同意大幅增加进入加沙的药品数量</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 21:25:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/qatar-confirms-medicine-for-israeli-hostages-will-enter-gaza-on-wednesday/0000018d-141e-d260-aded-b7be3dd40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长不停地从一个血腥恐怖场景跳到另一个场景</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-minister-keeps-dancing-from-one-bloody-terror-scene-to-another/0000018d-13e3-d727-a3cf-73e37f700000</link><description>周二，我们看到了另一场令人作呕的景象，就在一天前，教育部长 Yoav Kisch 在一次恐怖袭击现场加入了一群十几岁男孩的喧闹舞蹈，其中一名妇女被谋杀，另外 17 人受伤，其中许多人伤势严重。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 21:08:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-minister-keeps-dancing-from-one-bloody-terror-scene-to-another/0000018d-13e3-d727-a3cf-73e37f700000</guid></item><item><title>世界认真解决巴以冲突吗？我们最好希望如此</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/is-the-world-serious-about-solving-the-israel-palestine-conflict-wed-better-hope-so/0000018d-1345-d260-aded-b7ed9aa70000</link><description>“我们不会回到 10 月 6 日”是目前驻中东的外国使节的常见说法。但是，这是什么意思？世界对该地区的战后未来有何设想？两国解决方案如何融入其中？</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 20:32:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/is-the-world-serious-about-solving-the-israel-palestine-conflict-wed-better-hope-so/0000018d-1345-d260-aded-b7ed9aa70000</guid></item><item><title>贝埃里基布兹宣布以色列人质伊泰·斯维尔斯基和尤西·沙拉比死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi-killed-during-captivity-in-gaza/0000018d-13ce-d727-a3cf-73efc2360000</link><description>贝埃里基布兹宣布这一消息之前，哈马斯周日发布了一段视频，视频中两人与另一名以色列人质诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani) 在一起</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 20:25:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-hostages-itay-svirsky-and-yossi-sharabi-killed-during-captivity-in-gaza/0000018d-13ce-d727-a3cf-73efc2360000</guid></item><item><title>对于阿拉伯以色列人来说，即使是战时的爱国主义也不能抵御赤裸裸的种族主义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-16/ty-article/.highlight/for-arab-israelis-even-wartime-patriotism-is-not-a-shield-from-unvarnished-racism/0000018d-12e3-dd15-a7af-9eef0a6f0000</link><description>人们会想象，如果在战争期间不支持以色列会损害阿拉伯-以色列妇女的职业生涯，那么，相反，那些支持以色列事业的人将会得到奖励，而不是受到惩罚。但本周有关电视名人露西·阿哈里什的新闻显示出对阿拉伯人的敌意跨越了政治界限</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 19:09:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-16/ty-article/.highlight/for-arab-israelis-even-wartime-patriotism-is-not-a-shield-from-unvarnished-racism/0000018d-12e3-dd15-a7af-9eef0a6f0000</guid></item><item><title>沙特外长表示，如果巴勒斯坦问题得到解决，利雅得可能会承认以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-01-16/ty-article/saudi-foreign-minister-says-riyadh-could-recognize-israel-if-palestinian-issued-resolved/0000018d-12f7-dd15-a7af-9eff2d6e0000</link><description>费萨尔亲王在达沃斯世界经济论坛会议上表示，加沙停火是首要任务，和平只能通过“巴勒斯坦国”实现</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 18:56:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-01-16/ty-article/saudi-foreign-minister-says-riyadh-could-recognize-israel-if-palestinian-issued-resolved/0000018d-12f7-dd15-a7af-9eff2d6e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列当局为南部撤离人员预订了双重酒店，部分人被告知离开</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-authorities-double-book-hotel-for-southern-evacuees-some-told-to-leave/0000018d-12f2-dd15-a7af-9eff5f3b0000</link><description>政府将斯德洛特撤离人员在酒店的住宿期限延长至2月底，但酒店已经为基布兹马根撤离人员预订了一月底的住宿。一名仅提前两周通知就被告知离开的撤离者表示，“我们不知所措”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 16:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-authorities-double-book-hotel-for-southern-evacuees-some-told-to-leave/0000018d-12f2-dd15-a7af-9eff5f3b0000</guid></item><item><title>《辛贝特法》备忘录将使以色列安全机构能够监视记者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/memorandum-of-shin-bet-law-will-enable-israels-security-agency-to-spy-on-journalists/0000018d-12b9-d260-aded-b7b996f10000</link><description>该法律授权情报机构在计算机、手机所有者不知情的情况下对其进行秘密搜查。虽然一些职业在备忘录中受到保护，但记者却不受保护。民权组织称备忘录“忽视了政治影响力的危险”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 16:16:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/memorandum-of-shin-bet-law-will-enable-israels-security-agency-to-spy-on-journalists/0000018d-12b9-d260-aded-b7b996f10000</guid></item><item><title>艾美奖与会者对以色列-加沙战争双方表示声援</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/emmy-attendees-express-solidarity-for-both-sides-of-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018d-128a-d041-a3dd-5eeaaf020000</link><description>“佩戴具有象征意义的黄丝带不仅具有人类的力量，而且还可以上镜” ■ 演员和业界人士佩戴各种别针，包括黄丝带、鸽子，甚至国际法院的鳞片，以表达对以色列与哈马斯战争的看法</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 14:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/emmy-attendees-express-solidarity-for-both-sides-of-the-israel-gaza-war/0000018d-128a-d041-a3dd-5eeaaf020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家监管机构发现国防部多年来忽视患有创伤后应激障碍的残疾退伍军人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-watchdogs-find-defense-ministry-has-neglected-disabled-veterans-with-ptsd/0000018d-1169-de9c-a3df-7bf9a2a60000</link><description>国家审计长发现，用于扩大康复部门的预算的很大一部分尚未得到利用，以色列国防军退伍军人不了解自己的权利，并受到官僚主义障碍和缺乏数字访问的困扰</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 14:47:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-watchdogs-find-defense-ministry-has-neglected-disabled-veterans-with-ptsd/0000018d-1169-de9c-a3df-7bf9a2a60000</guid></item><item><title>教育部因阿拉伯以色列东道主而撤回对犹太活动的资助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-education-ministry-withdraws-funding-of-jewish-event-over-arab-israeli-host/0000018d-1216-d94e-abcf-3bf65cd70000</link><description>“代表异族通婚的女性不能代表犹太文化”，该部在谈到记者兼主持人露西·阿哈里什时表示，她的丈夫是犹太法乌达明星查希·哈勒维。主办“促进多元化、进步和自由犹太教”年度活动的以色列理事会要求该部撤回其决定</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 12:43:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/israeli-education-ministry-withdraws-funding-of-jewish-event-over-arab-israeli-host/0000018d-1216-d94e-abcf-3bf65cd70000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日100天后，加沙边境社区的以色列居民再也无法抑制愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/100-days-after-oct-7-israeli-residents-of-gaza-communities-cannot-hold-back-their-anger/0000018d-119f-d71c-ad9f-539f6aa70000</link><description>“你抛弃了我们直至死亡，我们的世界在你的注视下化为尘土” ■ 饱受蹂躏的加沙边境基布兹的“愤怒”幸存者聚集在以色列议会外，要求政府辞职</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 11:59:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/100-days-after-oct-7-israeli-residents-of-gaza-communities-cannot-hold-back-their-anger/0000018d-119f-d71c-ad9f-539f6aa70000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列军队决定给出详细答复时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/when-the-israeli-army-decides-to-give-a-detailed-answer/0000018d-11de-dac4-a9cf-53ffa52b0000</link><description>在战争期间经常发生的爆炸房屋内有居住者的情况中，以色列国防军倾向于保持含糊不清以掩盖“附带损害”的严重程度</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 11:21:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/when-the-israeli-army-decides-to-give-a-detailed-answer/0000018d-11de-dac4-a9cf-53ffa52b0000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特：伊朗利用以色列人拍摄安全官员的家，影响公众</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-iran-used-israelis-to-photo-security-officials-homes-influence-the-public/0000018d-0ed6-db13-affd-7ff79e500000</link><description>《辛贝特》证实了《国土报》的调查，调查显示伊朗情报机构运营煽动以色列人相互对抗、甚至招募以色列人的团体和页面，并揭露了至少另外三人</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:38:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-iran-used-israelis-to-photo-security-officials-homes-influence-the-public/0000018d-0ed6-db13-affd-7ff79e500000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗称袭击了以色列驻伊拉克“摩萨德总部”，为加沙战争中“其指挥官被杀”报仇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-attacked-israel-mossad-hq-in-iraq-to-avenge-the-killings-of-its-commanders/0000018d-116d-d71c-ad9f-53ef2bb80000</link><description>在伊朗声称摧毁了位于埃尔比勒的“摩萨德间谍总部”后，美国和法国谴责这次袭击是对伊拉克半自治库尔德斯坦主权的“鲁莽”和“令人担忧的侵犯”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 10:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-attacked-israel-mossad-hq-in-iraq-to-avenge-the-killings-of-its-commanders/0000018d-116d-d71c-ad9f-53ef2bb80000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争期间，以色列的民主衰落并未停止。在很多方面，情况变得更糟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-gaza-war-hasnt-stopped-israels-democratic-decline-in-many-ways-it-made-it-worse/0000018d-0dd4-d71c-ad9f-4fd64c7b0000</link><description>更多的监控、更多的枪支、更少的言论自由：内塔尼亚胡的联盟在 10 月 7 日的袭击后停止了削弱司法机构的计划，但战争却让它在没有这些的情况下实现了许多目标</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 09:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-gaza-war-hasnt-stopped-israels-democratic-decline-in-many-ways-it-made-it-worse/0000018d-0dd4-d71c-ad9f-4fd64c7b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/idf-releases-name-of-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-1181-de9c-a3df-7bf982c90001</link><description>21 岁的尼赞·谢斯勒 (Nitzan Schessler) 来自哈德拉 (Hadera)，周一在加沙南部的战斗中身亡。 37 岁的诺姆·阿什拉姆 (Noam Ashram) 周二因 12 月在加沙中部的战斗中受伤而死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 09:25:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-16/ty-article/idf-releases-name-of-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-1181-de9c-a3df-7bf982c90001</guid></item></channel></rss>